import React, { useState } from "react";
import { ThemeProvider, Modal, Div, Row, Col, Button, Text, Container, Icon } from "atomize";
import NetflixModal from "./NetflixModal"

function MyCliques() {
  const [modal, showModal] = useState(false)

  return(
    <Row d="flex" justify="space-around">
      <Row>
        <Col size="2">
          <Text
            textSize="subheading"
            textColor="black"
            fontFamily="code"
            textWeight="700"
          >
            MY CLIQUES
          </Text>
        </Col>



        <Col size="2">
          <Icon
            name="Add"
            color="black"
            size="24px"
          />
          <Text
            textSize="subheading"
            textColor="black"
            fontFamily="code"
            textWeight="700"
          >
            ADD NEW CLIQUES
          </Text>
        </Col>
      </Row>
      <NetflixModal
        isOpen={modal}
        onClose={() => showModal(false)}
      />
    </Row>
  )
}

export default MyCliques;
